"Pretty Little Liars" star Lucy Hale has a new project in the works post-Rosewood. According to Entertainment Weekly, she's set to star in a dark comedy for The CW called "Life Sentence." Beyond thankful for new ventures and opportunities !! https://t.co/OHJx4I9Npw The show is about a girl with terminal cancer who lives her final days to the fullest only to discover she actually isn't sick. Now, she must somehow cope with the life choices she made when she was living each day as if it were her last. It certainly sounds like an interesting plot with a lot of twists and drama in the works. We'll be keeping an eye out!